<item>
            <title>[LU-12809] recovery-small/110k gets stuck at client umount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12809</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;this happens because umount calls into statfs() which in turn waits for MDS2 stopped by the test:&lt;br/&gt;
	stop mds2 || error &quot;stop mds2 failed&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
	umount $MOUNT&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;statfs() is supposed to be &quot;lazy&quot; as per Andreas&apos;s comment in skype, but it is not for connections to MDSs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
